Here are some photos on how the project was assembled.
PARTS USED
1.ESP32 type C 30 pin type
2.TP4056 type C chaging Board
3.3.7V 18650 Cell Li-ion Rechargeable Battery
4.SSD1306 0.96inch 128x64 OLED Display Module
5.M274 360 Degrees Rotary Encoder Module Brick Sensor Switch Development KY-040
6.3.7V to 12V Mini DC-DC Boost Step Up Converter Board Module 5V/ 8V/ 9V 12V Output (Output set to 5V)
7.2-Pin Mini Rocker Switch
8.Tactile Switch Push Buttons 12mm
9.IR LED
10.IR Reciever
11.20OHMS current limiting resister for IR LED
12.1MOHMS X2 for voltage Divider
13.0.1uf Ceramic Capacitor for singnal filtering where needed
14.2N2222 NPN Switching Transistor for IR LED
15.330OHMS resistor for transister
16.Patience
17.Wires lots and lots of wires
